    {
      "id": "PopularPost181681",
      "post_content": "When casting any ![Variable Colorless](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=X&type=symbol) spell you first announce what ![Variable Colorless](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=X&type=symbol) will be, then you pay the cost of the spell. Any Medallion you have in play (or any other way of reducing costs) are applied before the payment. So if you cast [Endless Scream](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Endless Scream) with [Jet Meddallion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jet Meddallion) you control on battlefield, you announce what ![Variable Colorless](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=X&type=symbol) will be. If you say it's ![5](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=5&type=symbol) you pay ![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) for the spell.  \n  \nThis even works with spells that need specific mana. With two Jet Meddaliions on battlefield your 5 point [Drain Life](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drain Life) would cost ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) to pay.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost181681\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">When casting any <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Variable Colorless\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=X&amp;type=symbol\"/> spell you first announce what <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Variable Colorless\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=X&amp;type=symbol\"/> will be, then you pay the cost of the spell. Any Medallion you have in play (or any other way of reducing costs) are applied before the payment. So if you cast <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Endless Scream\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Endless Scream\">Endless Scream</a> with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jet Meddallion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jet Meddallion\">Jet Meddallion</a> you control on battlefield, you announce what <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Variable Colorless\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=X&amp;type=symbol\"/> will be. If you say it's <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"5\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=5&amp;type=symbol\"/> you pay <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"4\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=4&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> for the spell.<br/><br/>This even works with spells that need specific mana. With two Jet Meddaliions on battlefield your 5 point <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Drain Life\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drain Life\">Drain Life</a> would cost <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> to pay.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '181681'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (7/23/2011 5:08:53 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img